result.name: Nang kee

reviews.text: Tasty roasted goose with value for money deal

Price not high.  Roast goose was juicy with soft meat.  However, my company considered geese' skin not crispy but I found it fit my appetite.  Rice noodles (瀨粉) were of good quality.  Car parking there was convenient and only cost $20 each car (c.f. $30 for customers of Yue Kee 裕記).

One minor thing is that the queue for dining there was shorter than another renowned roast goose restaurant namely Yue Kee 裕記.
Nice choice of dishes, but the stur fried vegetables were too oily

Best goose in town, hands down! The seafood is also surprisingly good, from the stir-fried crab to the salt and pepper squid. Yes, it's a little far from the city but well worth the trek if you crave some goose
Great roast goose but not easily accessible for the tourist

result.adr_address: 香港深井深康路13號
result.name: 能記燒鵝飯店

reviews.text:
這裡的食物很差，我想是深井中的食市中最差的一員:腐乳通茶……簡直是白烚通茶、煎
藕餅……是煎粉餅、砵酒生蚝……沒砵酒豆粉蚝、燒鵝…….凍及死實、星洲米……比星洲湯米好少少、焯鵝腸……沒鵝味及好像收藏了很久、蒜泥蒸蝦……新鲜。最好的算白哈雲耳勝瓜……因煑法簡單，用手工。😱😱🤮🤮而且也便宜。
鵝，第一件還趁熱皮還可以，之後越食越無引
深井燒鵝，在深井有很多家，能記是其一，當然好吃，這區的燒鵝已變成經香港特色之一，繁忙時段泊車還是比較困難。
燒鵝正，還是用炭燒烤，味道一流，再者，其它如 椒鹽鮮魷 、脆皮豆腐都一樣好味道
招呼很好，食品味道為深井幾家燒鹅店最差的，由其隻燒鹅味道太鹹煙熏味道太重不似碳烧的。鹅的口肉質太老皮不夠脆。
